listings.title: design, develop or redesign your business wix website
listings.comment:
I was really sceptic as i had a bad fiverr expperience with an other website before. But I was so wrong. Fiaz was just so patient, he did everything I asked for and was just so really amazingly helpful with all I struggeled. I really appreciate the time you took to build my website. I am beyond happy. Cant wait to build my other website in a few weeks with you!

Thank you! Tanja

listings.title: design, develop or redesign your business wix website
listings.comment: Fiaz Tariq showcased good work in website development, yet there are areas for growth, particularly in aligning with professional standards and closer client expectations. While it was generally pleasant collaborating with Fiaz, improvements in politeness, response time, and understanding client needs could enhance the experience.

listings.title: design, develop or redesign your business wix website
listings.comment: I'd like everyone to know, in my search for a designer I was looking for designs and functionality that was very difficult and very in depth to understand.  Fiaz informed me that whatever my ask was that he would exceed expectations.  He has done that and more.  Not only did he exceed expectations, I learned a great deal from him as he was willing to teach me things about Wix that as a new ecommerce business owner I did not yet understand.  I highly recommend hiring this talented designer.... but don't take up too much of his time because I will need him for alot more of my own projects 💯

listings.title: design, develop or redesign your business wix website
listings.comment:
Fiaz was incredibly helpful and so patient with me as I'm not very familiar with Wix or any technical terminology. I gave him very little information to begin with and somehow he just understood exactly what I was looking for.
He created my website even better than I imagined it and he joined a call with me as well, taking the time to listen to my requests after the first draft.
Thank you Fiaz for your patience and your great energy and approach to your work. I sincerely appreciate your help with this!

listings.title: design, develop or redesign your business wix website
listings.comment: I can’t put in words how much I like working with Fiaz on this project. I know I probably wasn’t the easiest client to work with but he really didn’t let me feel like I was. He didn’t ever rush me or rush his work and did everything in a timely manner. I have more projects in the future and I’m glad I found someone i can work with for now on! I recommend 1000x
